<paragraph id="8BBC36F3FF90FFC15CB1FDDE8D440E95" blockId="1.[174,1233,379,687]" pageId="1" pageNumber="114">D i a g n o s i s. This species can be recognized from the combination of frons yellow above lunule, pruinose yellow or brown propleuron, yellow postpronotal lobe and notopleural triangle, and one pair of dorsocentral setae.</paragraph>
